    "Title": "Restore Order at ~mission(DefendLocationWrapperLocation)",
    "Description": "Our crew at <EM4>~mission(DefendLocationWrapperLocation|Address)</EM4> needs help. Enemy ships are swarming the area and attacking anything and everything they can find. That\u2019d be bad enough as is, but this site has some absolutely crucial gear and personnel that we can\u2019t have destroyed or compromised. \n\nConsidering the size and scale of the attack, you\u2019re gonna need a fully supplied ship and some reliable wingmen. Gather your crew, fly out to the site, and I\u2019ll send you specifics on where you\u2019re needed most.\n\nTo prove just how serious we are about getting this done right, the main contractor will earn a bonus <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount) Council Scrip</EM4> for making sure absolutely nothing goes wrong.\n\n- Stow",
